      "Back-line single-edge assault (north only)",
      "Glacier tanks + frostshade chill",
      "Twin south-rim shelf-keeps"
    ]
  },
  "intro": [
    {
      "title": "Anchorfall Twin",
      "lines": [
        "The shelf cracked in two when the anchor fell. Two keeps now, one line.",
        "Nothing comes from behind — the rear ice is sound. They pour down from the north.",
        "Frostshades drift the gap between the holds. The glacier just keeps walking."
      ],
      "art": "siege"
    }
  ],
  "outro": [
    {
      "title": "The Line Held",
      "lines": [
        "Eight dawns of snow and grinding ice. Both keeps still stand the watch.",
        "The shelf is quiet again, and the cold belongs to no one."
      ],
      "art": "dawn"
    }
